---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: "/colophon/"
title: Colofão
---
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-inner page-hero-inner--editorial">
    <div class="editorial-bar">
      <a href="/sitemap/" class="editorial-back" aria-label="Voltar para mapa do site"><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
      <div class="editorial-brand">
        <p class="editorial-site">{{ site.name }}</p>
        <p class="editorial-hello">Como este site foi feito</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-frame">
  <div class="content-surface">
    <header class="entry-header-card">
      {% set breadcrumb = [{label: "Colofão"}] %}
      {% include "partials/breadcrumb.njk" %}
      <h1 class="entry-title">Colofão</h1>
      <p class="entry-summary">Stack, ferramentas, fontes e decisões técnicas por trás deste site.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="uses-section" style="border-top:none;padding-top:0">
      <h2 class="uses-section-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt" aria-hidden="true"></i> Geração e templates</h2>
      <div class="uses-grid">
        <div class="uses-card">
          <div class="uses-card-icon" style="background:color-mix(in srgb,#c0b000 12%,var(--bg-card))">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt" style="color:#c0b000" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="uses-card-body">
            <p class="uses-card-name">Eleventy 3.0+</p>
            <p class="uses-card-desc">Gerador de site estático minimalista em Node.js. Sem framework de frontend.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="uses-card">
          <div class="uses-card-icon" style="background:color-mix(in srgb,#e07b54 12%,var(--bg-card))">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-file-code" style="color:#e07b54" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="uses-card-body">
            <p class="uses-card-name">Nunjucks</p>
            <p class="uses-card-desc">Engine de templates para layouts, partials e lógica de views.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="uses-section">
      <h2 class="uses-section-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-palette" aria-hidden="true"></i> Estilos e UI</h2>
      <div class="uses-grid">
        <div class="uses-card">
          <div class="uses-card-icon" style="background:color-mix(in srgb,#06b6d4 12%,var(--bg-card))">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-wind" style="color:#06b6d4" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="uses-card-body">
            <p class="uses-card-name">Tailwind CSS</p>
            <p class="uses-card-desc">Utilitários de layout. Todo o design system usa CSS custom properties nativas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="uses-card">
          <div class="uses-card-icon" style="background:color-mix(in srgb,#528bff 12%,var(--bg-card))">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-icons" style="color:#528bff" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="uses-card-body">
            <p class="uses-card-name">Font Awesome 7.0</p>
            <p class="uses-card-desc">Iconografia via CDN. Solid e Brands em todo o site.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="uses-card">
          <div class="uses-card-icon" style="background:color-mix(in srgb,#4a90d9 12%,var(--bg-card))">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-font" style="color:#4a90d9" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="uses-card-body">
            <p class="uses-card-name">Inter</p>
            <p class="uses-card-desc">Tipografia principal via Google Fonts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="uses-section">
      <h2 class="uses-section-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-cloud-arrow-up" aria-hidden="true"></i> Publicação e versionamento</h2>
      <div class="uses-grid">
        <div class="uses-card">
          <div class="uses-card-icon" style="background:color-mix(in srgb,#181717 12%,var(--bg-card))">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-github" style="color:var(--text-primary)" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="uses-card-body">
            <p class="uses-card-name">GitHub</p>
            <p class="uses-card-desc">Repositório público. Código-fonte aberto sob <a href="https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AGPL-3.0</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="uses-card">
          <div class="uses-card-icon" style="background:color-mix(in srgb,#00C7B7 12%,var(--bg-card))">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-cloud-arrow-up" style="color:#00C7B7" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="uses-card-body">
            <p class="uses-card-name">Netlify</p>
            <p class="uses-card-desc">Deploy automático a cada push na branch main.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="uses-section">
      <h2 class="uses-section-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-satellite-dish" aria-hidden="true"></i> IndieWeb e feeds</h2>
      <div class="uses-grid">
        <div class="uses-card">
          <div class="uses-card-icon" style="background:color-mix(in srgb,#f26522 12%,var(--bg-card))">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-rss" style="color:#f26522" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="uses-card-body">
            <p class="uses-card-name">Feed Atom</p>
            <p class="uses-card-desc">Feed único em <a href="/feed.xml">/feed.xml</a> cobrindo todas as 11 coleções do site.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="uses-card">
          <div class="uses-card-icon" style="background:color-mix(in srgb,#c47db8 12%,var(--bg-card))">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-share-nodes" style="color:#c47db8" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="uses-card-body">
            <p class="uses-card-name">Microformatos + Webmentions</p>
            <p class="uses-card-desc">h-card e h-entry nas páginas. <a href="https://webmention.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">webmention.io</a> para receber menções.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="uses-section">
      <h2 class="uses-section-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-robot" aria-hidden="true"></i> Desenvolvimento assistido</h2>
      <div class="uses-grid">
        <div class="uses-card">
          <div class="uses-card-icon" style="background:color-mix(in srgb,#d97757 12%,var(--bg-card))">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-robot" style="color:#d97757" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="uses-card-body">
            <p class="uses-card-name">Claude (Anthropic)</p>
            <p class="uses-card-desc">Features, refatorações e decisões de arquitetura via Claude Code.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
